title: 插件汉化后报错
author: WhiteXFox
txt_content:
插件是JetsMinions5.7.15
汉化文本#汉化重制于2020/8/19
#JetsMinions5.7.15 汉化重制者White_Fox[白狐]
#QQ号:2654748330
#Messages
NoPermission: "&c你没有权限!"
NoPermissionForSkin: "&c你没有权限使用此皮肤" #Maybe put your buycraft / however the player gets skins :) - Placeholder %SKIN% can be used to get the skin identifier

ErrorOccurred: "&c发生未知错误，请立刻联系管理员!"

#If they try placing the minion in a no build zone, or similar:
CantPlaceMinionHere: "&c你不能把精灵放置在这里!"
#If there is a chunk limit set, this message is given if they are unable to place their minions due to that
ChunkMinionPlaceLimit: "&a你不能放置更多的精灵 %CHUNKLIMIT% 在这个区块!"

#The message that appears if the minion was successfully placed, although the action that the minion does is blocked
#(For example, placed next on the edge of spawn, and trying to get the minion to mine in spawn)
MinionCannotPerformHere: "&c精灵的能力在这里无法使用 (你确定在合适的位置放置了精灵？)"

#The message that appears when they click the 'rename' button in the UI
RenameMessage: "&e输入你给精灵取的名字，或输入 &cCancel&e 来取消"
RenameMessageCanceled: "&e精灵改名失败!"
RenameMessageSuccess: "&e成功将精灵的名字改为&f %NAME% #%NAME% will get the minions display name

MinionMustBeFullHealthToDestroy: "&c精灵必须饥饿度全满才能被收回!"

NotEnoughMoneyToHealMinion: "&C你的钱不够，你需要 $%MONEYNEEDED% 来购买它!"
HealSuccessful: "&C已给精灵增加 %HEALAMOUNT% 饥饿度"
HealNotNeeded: "&C精灵饥饿度已满，不需要再喂食它了!"
VaultNotInstalled: "&CVault未安装或版本过低，请立刻联系服务器管理员!"

NotEnoughMoneyToUpgradeMinion: "&c你没有足够的钱升级精灵!" #%MONEYNEEDED% can be used as a placeholder
MinionAlreadyMaxLevel: "&c这个精灵无法再升级了!"

#rotation
MinionRotatedMessage: "&a已将精灵朝向调整为 &e%DIRECTION%"

#Link a chest messages
LinkAChestMessage: "&a右键点击一个箱子来绑定它"
LinkAChestSuccess: "&a设置成功，精灵成功绑定了这个箱子"
LinkAChestUnattached: "&a绑定箱子已移除!"
LinkAChestFail: "&c设置绑定箱子已超时！下次请快一点右键点击箱子！"
LinkChestBroken: "&c你打破了一个绑定箱子!"

UnknownCommand: "&c未知指令"

#When /minions is entered - Placeholders %VERSION%
HelpCommand:
  - "&b&m---------------&r&e[ &e&l精灵 &a%VERSION% &e]&b&m---------------"
  - "&8/&aminions about &7- &f显示插件信息"
  - "&8/&aminions give {online_player} {minion_type} {amount} [level] &7- &f给玩家 [level]级 精灵"
  - "&8/&aminions reload &7- &f重载插件"
  - "&8/&aminions storeother {online_player} &7- &f为玩家打开商店"
  - "&8/&aminions store &7- &f打开精灵商店"
  - "&8汉化重置者 -by 白狐"

GivenMinion: "&a你获得了一个 &b%TYPE% &a精灵!" #Placeholders, %AMOUNT% and %TYPE%

MaxMinionAmount: "&c你不能再放置更多精灵了，已达到最大放置数量限制 %MAXAMOUNTALLOWED%" #placeholder will return the max minions allowed for that user

BreakMinionWithFullInventory: "&c你的背包已满，精灵已落在你的脚下!"

MinionNameMaxLength: "&c这个名字太长了!请短一点"

MinionExpGiven: "&A你从这只精灵身上收集了 &e%EXP% EXP"

MinionStoreNotEnoughMoney: "&c你的钱不够" #%MONEYNEEDED%,%MINIONTYPE% can be used as a placeholder
MinionStorePurchase: "&c你花费了 %MONEYNEEDED% 成功购买了 %MINIONTYPE% 精灵"

#Placeholders, %RANGEPLACED%, %REQUIREDRANGE%
MinionChestToFar: "&c你放置的距离大于了 %RANGEPLACED% , 距离最大是 %REQUIREDRANGE%"
